    <allowInChatterGroups>true</allowInChatterGroups>
    <compactLayoutAssignment>SYSTEM</compactLayoutAssignment>
    <deploymentStatus>Deployed</deploymentStatus>
    <description>It is essential for the business to be able to track current and historical Onboarding attempts on an account for a variety of reasons: KPIs, goals, success rate of each Onboarding attempt, YoY/MoM activation rates etc. When an account becomes a customer, a new SaaS and/or Billing Onboarding Attempt(s) is created. Once the attempt is Closed or Canceled (or any other closed status), the Attempt locks down and no future changes will be made to it.</description>
    <enableActivities>true</enableActivities>
    <enableBulkApi>true</enableBulkApi>
    <enableFeeds>false</enableFeeds>
    <enableHistory>true</enableHistory>
